  5. Forced Termination.

  If, as a consequence of a court judgment or allegation of patent
infringement or for any other reason, conditions are imposed on you
that contradict the conditions of this License, they do not excuse you
from the conditions of this License.  If you cannot use the Program
so as to satisfy simultaneously your obligations under this License
